node.text:
Voices of change, on and beyond the court. ✊
 
During last year’s NBA and WNBA seasons, @jaeecan and @jrue_holiday11 experienced the game of basketball in a way they never had before. They lived quarantined lives, played before hushed crowds, and perhaps most importantly—became public protestors for social justice. 

In this “One on One” conversation, the two space makers share what it was like to go through one of the most unique, challenging, and important moments in sport history, and come out on the other side, changed forever.

Link in bio to read more. 

🎨 @richchane
📝 @madsear

Congrats to the 2021 Kia NBA Defensive Player of the Year – Rudy Gobert

Nikola Jokic has blurred the lines of traditional basketball and paved another lane for evolution.
 
The Serbian second-round draft pick has defied convention throughout his career and redefined excellence along the way. A terrifying mismatch, outthinking his opponents and the perfect complement for all of his teammates - he’s been such a joy to watch and lucky for us, the journey’s just begun. 
 
Congrats to the 2021 Kia NBA MVP - Nikola Jokic
